<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE MEMORIES LIVE ON AFTER VOICE IS GONE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
For over 20 years, at work or at play, in my car or at the games, I'll always 
remember that famous bellowing voice announcing such superstars as Garvey, 
Wills, Chamberlain, West, Gabriel, Youngblood, Dionne and Berry. Whether I was 
in a good mood or bad, it was always a pleasure to hear that ever-present 
foghorn. 
</P>
<P>
Thanks for the memories, John Ramsey. 
</P>
<P>
JIMMIE SHAW, Hermosa Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
