A RIVERA OF TEARS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
When Geraldo Rivera confessed at the convention of the National Assn. of 
Television Program Executives, ("Geraldo Turns Up His Nose at Sensationalism," 
Jan. 18), that he "strayed," did he shed tears? Hurry, the world wonders. 
</P>
<P>
VAL RODRIGUEZ, Signal Hill 
