<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ACQUIRED IMMUNE DEFICIENCY SYNDROME; NEW YORK CITY -- SUITS; DOCTORS; 
NEGLIGENCE; HOSPITALS -- NEW YORK CITY; WASTE MATERIALS -- DISPOSAL; PREGO, 
VERONICA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
