<TEXT>
<P>
If someone tried to force a fundamentalist minister on a homosexual 
congregation, Luedtke would scream to high heaven. Yet she feels she has the 
right to try to force on other congregations ministers just as unwanted and 
just as unsuitable to them. 
</P>
<P>
