sinful. Besides their freedom of choice, there is, in fact, strong reason for 
accepting this teaching, since former homosexuals have stated that, based on 
that outlook they have been able to change "through Christ" ("The Gospel and 
the Gay," by K.O. Gangel). 
</P>
<P>
