<P>
FOOTBALL PLAYERS; DRAFT (SPORTS); FREE AGENTS (SPORTS); LOS ANGELES RAIDERS 
(FOOTBALL TEAM); MCELROY, VANN; PICKEL, BILL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
