Vargas. TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Three of Circus Vargas' 
clowns are, from left, Alturo, Lenny and Danny. The circus, which will be in 
Orange County through Feb. 15, employs a total of 12 clowns. ; Photo, Circus 
Vargas, now in 21st year, opened its tent flaps in Santa Ana Thursday, kicking 
off its two-week stay in Orange County. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
