POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; TRENDS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; LIBERAL DEMOCRATIC PARTY 
(JAPAN); KAIFU, TOSHIKI; ABE, SHINTARO; POLITICAL CORRUPTION; JAPAN -- TAXES 
</P>
