A doctor apparently trying to revive his wife who was suffering a fatal asthma 
attack collapsed and died of a heart attack, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
Paramedics found Betty Wrenn, 66, dead and her husband, Frank Wrenn, 67, 
slumped over her in cardiac arrest on the floor of their home Thursday, 
officials said. 
