<TEXT>
<P>
The New Orleans Health Department won't need to buy surgical gloves until 1995 
or so, thanks to a 400,000-pair gift from an importer. 
</P>
<P>
Suzy Shay of Direct China Trade Ltd. said $48,000 worth of latex gloves arrived 
from China too late for the customer for whom she had ordered them. 
</P>
<P>
Shay decided to donate the gloves to the city rather than find another buyer. 
